          <fn id="men13580-note-0010">
            <p>Contig count came from Table <xref rid="men13580-tbl-0008" ref-type="table">8</xref>. Number of loci was estimated from the distribution of <sc>blastn</sc> hits in the appropriate genome, with a minimum of 10,000 bases between loci.</p>
